  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to explore the effect of Transarterial Chemoembolization (TACE) on
      the prognosis of patients with microvascular invasion presence(MVI) and overexpression of
      Aspartate-β-hydroxylase(ASPH).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
